Swerve #2
Publisher:  Arcana Studios

Created by Jon Judy and Dexter Wee

Chapter 2 of 6. San Antonio, 1976: Eric Layton, desperate for cash, left college behind to dive into the world of pro-wrestling. From there, it was an easy slide into the underbelly of the "rasslin'" biz, where the box office and concession stand make for an easy way to launder drug money.
